{"tid":1704411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德記者形容港已成警察國家：比IS恐怖分子更可怕","createTime":"2019-11-10T16:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T00:52:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4471baff6cd061a2d6bbe7f7af35a4852774bc","tid":1704411,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"自6月反修例示威浪潮爆發，香港警隊在5個月以來的濫權濫暴，飽受全港以至國際上不同組織批評，警暴肆虐更成為了全球注視香港的原因。美國共和黨參議員Josh Hawley更直斥，警隊濫權令香港墮落成為一個警察國家（Police State）。今日（10日）多區再爆發警民衝突，一名來自德國的記者在社交媒體大讚香港示威者有禮貌，同時指自己害怕香港警察多於恐怖分子。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191111/60252387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191111%2F60252387&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=5dcfda1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191111%2F60252387&h=5305a35a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191111/60252387</a>"},{"pid":"94599cfebb07f0444f8c23b17d96a54e870cbd44","tid":1704411,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc45b22d76916f9f3368d5ff82c4fbe1f7ca0d7","tid":1704411,"uid":50361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}